        "category": "ancestry",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>By landing your foot orb directly on the ground, you can use your momentum to bounce yourself forward. If you land on the ground at the end of a jump (whether performing a [[/act high-jump]], [[/act long-jump]], or @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.actions.Item.Leap]), you can use High Jump or Long Jump as a single action, but you don't get to Stride as part of the activity.</p><hr /><p><strong>Special</strong> If you have the @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.feats.Item.Quick Jump] skill feat, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to your Athletics check for your second High Jump or Long Jump.</p>"
        },
